  "description": "The snare voice deconstructed into pure noise atmosphere. Long 1.8-second decay, heavy reverb, near-zero body — the noise component is the whole event. Three voices layered: snare, clap, and a high-pitched percussive wash. Not a snare hit — a weather system passing through. Best heard solo at low velocity.",
